  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the partisans got the-- the railway ride, you see, here and there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we-- we came to that [INAUDIBLE] town there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then we had friends there, and one of the guards, who was a-- a guard.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we-- we were in a-- in a cattle train.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A cattle train, that's how they shipped the prisoners.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One-- one of the guards-- it was a, really, a friendly, friendly guard-- guy, you see?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And by the time we got into-- oh, what was the name of that [INAUDIBLE] town there?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But anyway, his-- his wife was with-- with the three other-- other women who were waiting-- waiting already-- waiting already with food baskets, you see, with some-- some food.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And well, in the meantime, there was seven American pilots, who were shot-- shot don't over there and-- and was put in the same prison.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were in-- they were in the same group with us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Finally, we arrived in Budapest in-- in the late evening.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was one-- one woman among-- in-- in our group, from [NON-ENGLISH] prison.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was taken away to the-- to the [NON-ENGLISH] prison.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Hannah was also in-- in-- in a-- in a prison.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, she was-- from that prison, she was transferred up to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was-- then she was shot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I met in my-- in my research then, I was-- I met some of these people, even that woman that Hannah was in the same-- same prison for-- for-- for a month.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And met a boy-- boy who was the neighbors from-- from school times.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so-- so my book is pretty well-- pretty well-- But it-- please tell me, when you arrived to the-- to the prison in Budapest, what happened?",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
